{"tid":874201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"正妹再挑戰清真寺野外露出　全裸滾地毯不怕被逮 大圖","createTime":"2018-10-24T04:30:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T05:54:26.000Z","uid":72009,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0356784315be93bd78fce3a400499ace48079801","tid":874201,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T04:30:15.000Z","msg":"美國一名女子帕本(Marisa Papen)，不斷挑戰各國文化與法律極限，堅持她的「超自然生活」。這一次她又再度做出「創舉」，前進土耳其伊斯坦堡，竟然直接在清真寺大膽野外露出，讓眾人看見她的下體恥毛，甚至拍攝一系列全裸滾地毯的照片。但帕本說，她不怕因此被逮捕。<br />\n據英國《每日星報》報導，這次帕本前進聖索菲亞大教堂(Hagia Sophia)進行野外露出拍攝，聖索菲亞大教堂是伊斯坦堡著名的地標，也是重要的歷史建築物，已經有1500年的歷史。這次帕本不畏人來人往的信徒與遊客，就直接在聖索菲亞大教堂外的一處角落，當眾野外露出。此外，帕本也拍攝一系列「全裸滾地毯」的照片，只見帕本依舊不遮點，直接裸體張腿拍攝。<br />\n帕本的信念就是「把衣服脫了，挑戰宗教專制」。她說，現在許多人受到政府或宗教的心靈禁錮，因此她強調自然裸體，就是希望帶領人們能從中獲得自由與解放。雖然帕本去年到埃及老寺廟全裸，遭到逮捕並坐牢，但她仍無所畏懼，陸續在以色列哭牆附近的地點全裸露點曬日頭，甚至下體夾住懸掛以色列國旗的旗桿攀爬。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181024/1453181\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181024%2F1453181&d=PLqY17On9GjrtTpqPr5A8QRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=d9265b4a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181024%2F1453181&h=af323061\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181024/1453181</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181024/640_43b3bad3d32ae6f51e2cb9ba1d8f2970.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181024%2F640_43b3bad3d32ae6f51e2cb9ba1d8f2970.jpg&h=6bdf3289&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181024/640_551e94f48f7dcbdf45ed4ea9d4743b11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181024%2F640_551e94f48f7dcbdf45ed4ea9d4743b11.jpg&h=989b9210&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181024/640_df067c93069ece12dbcd79bea800705d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181024%2F640_df067c93069ece12dbcd79bea800705d.jpg&h=f5e5e152&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd05fe0a30fafe55484f787f2df035ac1121404d","tid":874201,"uid":35841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T05:07:11.000Z","msg":"個樣同身材<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c92f7522194398af959d15dfe05aa6e8e2a3e241","tid":874201,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T05:14:52.000Z","msg":"去左強姦大國未？"},{"pid":"d2464eac9dad015c852edb7b3a3732dbcc90ada1","tid":874201,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T05:23:20.000Z","msg":"身體自主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc0fc0ef7f9c4338d81f404681b0486bb600d7cd","tid":874201,"uid":41311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T05:54:26.000Z","msg":"草地滾傳球"}]}